Module simulation.animal_simulation
Package simulation.animal_simulation

Class SimulationSettings

java.lang.Object
simulation.animal_simulation.SimulationSettings
public class SimulationSettings extends Object
The SimulationSettings class holds the settings for the animal simulation. It includes properties such as map size, grass amount, thick vegetation amount, rabbit and fox shelter IDs, timeout between simulation steps, and a flag for enabling logs.

This class provides methods to set these properties, as well as to export the current settings into a JSON file and import settings from a JSON file.
